Cell["\<\
Next-step probabilities will be determined by the directional derivatives of \
a scalar field, which\[LongDash]with linear  corrugation in mind\[LongDash]we \
will take initially to be given by the y-invariant function\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.534968658253529*^9, 3.53496875769862*^9}}],

